import React from 'react'; import { PDFViewer, PDFDownloadLink, Document, Page, Text, View, Font, Image } from '@react-pdf/renderer'; import { styles } from '../styles/resumeStyles'; Font.register({ family: 'NanumGothic', src: 'https://fonts.gstatic.com/ea/nanumgothic/v5/NanumGothic-Regular.ttf', fontStyle: 'normal', fontWeight: 'normal' }); const ResumeDocument = ({ formData }) => ( 접수번호: _____________ 노인일자리 신청서 성명 {formData.name} 연락처 {formData.mobilePhone} {formData.photo && ( )} 주민등록번호 {formData.residentNumber1}-{formData.residentNumber2} 주소 {formData.address} {formData.detailAddress} 최종학력 {formData.education} 세대구성 {formData.householdType} {(formData.spouse || formData.children || formData.grandchildren) && ( ` (동거가족: ${[ formData.spouse && '배우자', formData.children && `자녀 ${formData.childrenCount}명`, formData.grandchildren && `손자녀 ${formData.grandchildrenCount}명` ].filter(Boolean).join(', ')})` )} 경제상태 {`${formData.economicStatus} / 기초생활수급자: ${formData.basicLivingRecipient}`} 건강상태 {formData.healthStatus} 희망직종 1순위: {formData.desiredPrograms.first} {formData.desiredPrograms.second && ( 2순위: {formData.desiredPrograms.second} )} {formData.desiredPrograms.third && ( 3순위: {formData.desiredPrograms.third} )} 신청동기 {formData.applicationMotives.join(', ')} 참여경력 {formData.workExperience.isNew ? `참여경력 있음 (${formData.workExperience.years.join(', ')}년)` : '신규참여'} ); const ResumeTemplate = ({ formData }) => { const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false); return (
} fileName={`${formData.name}_노인일자리신청서.pdf`} className="hmk-button hmk-download-button" > {({ blob, url, loading, error }) => loading ? '문서 생성중...' : 'PDF 다운로드' }
); }; export default ResumeTemplate;
